Usage: saveBlackBox [-help] [-lefFile <string>] { <instName> | -all } [ -5.6 ]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<instName>            # Specifies the name of the blackbox instance.
                      # (string, optional)
-5.6                  #   (bool, optional)
-all                  # Specifies all blackbox instances. (bool, optional)
-lefFile <string>     # Specifies the LEF filename. If you do not specify a
                      # name, the default is cellTypeName.lef. (string, optional)